This is the main repository for the TDD extreme startup workshop.

To build code and run unit-tests, execute:  "./gradle test"

To participate in workshop, do the following:
1. Create git account
2. Fork the repository git@github.com:asolntsev/tdd-workshop.git
3. Create class with your name, see ChuckNorris.java and BruceLee.java for example.
   - Your class should extend ee.devclub.extremestartup.Workshop
   - Your class should implement method answer()
4. Commit & push changes to your forked repository
5. Send a pull request to git@github.com:asolntsev/tdd-workshop.git

Workshop master will merge your changes to the main repository and run his tests against your code.